{"blocks":[{"key":"djjks","text":"Add an equal volumen of ChCl:IAA and vortex x 30 sec","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dl10g","text":" ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"4gc0u","text":"Extract the WHOLE aquose phase, do not leave any of it from each tube.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2s3jm","text":"ignore any coloration of the aqueus phase","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":6},{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":41}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cnc0r","text":"*Optional : Gycogen can be added at this point","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":0,"length":46}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"58o5a","text":"Transfer the phase to 1.5 ml tubes and add 1/4 volume of 10M LiCl and mix by inverting","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7f4gs","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"8F1CE140A0B611EDAD390F343B970A94","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}}}}
